Surf_santorini ported from CSGO to CSS!

A fun little Tier 1 map taking place in the ocean amongst animals and palms. Map features 5 bonuses aswell all made by myself. 

If birds cause issues do this in ur stripper file: 

filter: {
"model" "models/props_critters/seagull_group.mdl"
}

Zoners / admins:

Same as all my maps. Trigger_multiple.

mapstart - mapend
s2s s3s s4s s5s s6s s7s s8s
b1s b1e, b2s b2e, b3s b3e, b4s b4e, b5s b5e

Have fun guys!
